summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the north 40 feet of Lots 5 and 6 and north 25 feet of Lots 7 and 8, Block 1, Town of Yesler Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-155 and 17-113, respectively.
